{"type":"text","timestamp":1783921477914,"sessionID":"ses_0a60505fdffeqSdEmZI11c4h43","part":{"id":"prt_f5a018170001RhVLpROQLRGK8D","messageID":"msg_f5a013ce0001DPJHy76jzobhA9","sessionID":"ses_0a60505fdffeqSdEmZI11c4h43","type":"text","text":"Iteration 1 confirmed one remaining blocking conformance mismatch: `code-webflow/references/shared/enforcement.md` places a five-link “Related Documents” block before `## 1. OVERVIEW`, contrary to R3’s H1 + 1–2 sentence intro + Overview ordering. The same corpus scan found a separate P2 class of eight lexical paths (five resolved documents) with three-sentence intros; all 163 documents otherwise pass the resource validator, frontmatter/version, filename, wrapper, and scoped-link checks.","time":{"start":1783921475952,"end":1783921477911},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c8a8f0db6a17b0b016a547b43f00c8191b0caf16036f0d1f8","phase":"commentary"}}}}
