ive content inserted before Overview; do not treat validator success alone as proof of R3 ordering.\n <!-- /ANCHOR:exhausted-approaches -->\n \n ## 9. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n \n@@ -58,10 +58,10 @@\n \n <!-- ANCHOR:next-focus -->\n ## 10. NEXT FOCUS\n \n-- Dimension: `correctness`\n-- Focus: deterministic current-state conformance across all configured Markdown paths, with direct rereads of prior structural findings.\n+- Dimension: `security`\n+- Focus: replay prior cookie/CDN guidance findings and inspect adjacent trust-boundary examples without repeating the structural sweep.\n <!-- /ANCHOR:next-focus -->\n \n <!-- ANCHOR:known-context -->\n ## 11. KNOWN CONTEXT\n@@ -70,18 +70,19 @@\n - Behavior claims: five-field frontmatter, four-part versions, snake_case names, H1/intro/Overview structure, preserved substantive content, and repaired in-hub references.\n - Reuse and conventions: create-skill reference/asset templates and `validate_document.py` are the named authorities.\n - Risk areas: earlier reviews found a missing Overview wrapper, overlong intros, tautological When-to-Use guidance, contradictory session-cookie guidance, and an under-constrained CDN loader; the packet now claims the in-scope structural items were fixed.\n - Missing context: Spec Kit Memory retrieval timed out; no packet-level `resource-map.md` exists.\n+- Iteration 1 carry-forward: `C1-P1-001` remains active at `code-webflow/references/shared/enforcement.md:19-24`; `C1-P2-001` covers eight lexical paths/five resolved documents with three-sentence intros.\n - Out of scope: surface `SKILL.md` header shape and unrelated deep-loop artifacts.\n <!-- /ANCHOR:known-context -->\n \n <!-- ANCHOR:cross-reference-status -->\n ## 12. CROSS-REFERENCE STATUS\n \n | Protocol | Level | Status | Notes |\n |----------|-------|--------|-------|\n-| `spec_code` | core | pending | Run in traceability iteration. |\n-| `checklist_evidence` | core | pending | Run in traceability iteration. |\n+| `spec_code` | core | fail (provisional) | Current R3 mismatch; replay in traceability iteration. |\n+| `checklist_evidence` | core | fail (provisional) | Validator evidence does not prove pre-Overview ordering. |\n | `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | pending | Classify from packet scope. |\n | `playbook_capability` | overlay | pending | Classify from packet scope. |\n <!-- /ANCHOR:cross-reference-status -->\n \n@@ -89,14 +90,14 @@\n ## 13. FILES UNDER REVIEW\n \n | Root | Paths | Status |\n |------|------:|--------|\n-| code-opencode references | 50 | pending |\n-| code-opencode assets | 15 | pending |\n-| code-webflow references | 86 | pending |\n-| code-webflow assets | 9 | pending |\n+| code-opencode references | 50 | correctness reviewed with P2 class |\n+| code-opencode assets | 15 | correctness reviewed clean |\n+| code-webflow references | 86 | correctness reviewed with P1/P2 findings |\n+| code-webflow assets | 9 | correctness reviewed clean |\n | code-quality references | 0 | notApplicable |\n-| code-quality assets | 3 | pending |\n+| code-quality assets | 3 | correctness reviewed clean |\n <!-- /ANCHOR:files-under-review -->\n \n <!-- ANCHOR:review-boundaries -->\n ## 14. REVIEW BOUNDARIES\n","additions":15,"deletions":14}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment/review/xhigh-confirm/lineages/confirm-c/logs/reduce-lineage.cjs\nA .opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment/review/xhigh-confirm/lineages/confirm-c/prompts/iteration-001.md\nA .opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment/review/xhigh-confirm/lineages/confirm-c/iterations/iteration-001.md\nA .opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment/review/xhigh-confirm/lineages/confirm-c/deltas/iter-001.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment/review/xhigh-confirm/lineages/confirm-c/deep-review-state.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment/r