{"type":"text","timestamp":1783921671337,"sessionID":"ses_0a60505fdffeqSdEmZI11c4h43","part":{"id":"prt_f5a0477b0001KNKh7tRIfCV4Gm","messageID":"msg_f5a044205001bTlWQfCGHJlysk","sessionID":"ses_0a60505fdffeqSdEmZI11c4h43","type":"text","text":"Iteration 2 found no new security defect. The prior cookie contradiction is fixed with an explicitly non-sensitive client cookie plus server-side `HttpOnly` guidance, and the prior CDN-loader issue is fixed with HTTPS host allowlisting and SRI guidance; adjacent script loaders use fixed constants or trusted-code parameters, with no demonstrated user-input path.","time":{"start":1783921670064,"end":1783921671335},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_015d57f4171ed821016a547c06075881919c07defec379f2a2","phase":"commentary"}}}}
