ce, contradictory session-cookie guidance, and an under-constrained CDN loader; the packet now claims the in-scope structural items were fixed.\n - Missing context: Spec Kit Memory retrieval timed out; no packet-level `resource-map.md` exists.\n - Iteration 1 carry-forward: `C1-P1-001` remains active at `code-webflow/references/shared/enforcement.md:19-24`; `C1-P2-001` covers eight lexical paths/five resolved documents with three-sentence intros.\n - Iteration 2 carry-forward: no new finding; the prior cookie and CDN guidance defects are resolved, while the active correctness P1/P2 remain unchanged.\n+- Iteration 3 carry-forward: `C3-P1-001` records the failed strict completion gate and 25 uncited completed items; both core protocols fail and both overlays are not applicable.\n - Out of scope: surface `SKILL.md` header shape and unrelated deep-loop artifacts.\n <!-- /ANCHOR:known-context -->\n \n <!-- ANCHOR:cross-reference-status -->\n ## 12. CROSS-REFERENCE STATUS\n \n | Protocol | Level | Status | Notes |\n |----------|-------|--------|-------|\n-| `spec_code` | core | fail (provisional) | Current R3 mismatch; replay in traceability iteration. |\n-| `checklist_evidence` | core | fail (provisional) | Validator evidence does not prove pre-Overview ordering. |\n-| `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | pending | Classify from packet scope. |\n-| `playbook_capability` | overlay | pending | Classify from packet scope. |\n+| `spec_code` | core | fail | R3 contradicted by `C1-P1-001`. |\n+| `checklist_evidence` | core | fail | Strict validation reports 25 completed items without evidence (`C3-P1-001`). |\n+| `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | notApplicable | Feature-catalog files and capability claims are outside scope. |\n+| `playbook_capability` | overlay | notApplicable | No playbook or runtime capability is in scope. |\n <!-- /ANCHOR:cross-reference-status -->\n \n <!-- ANCHOR:files-under-review -->\n ## 13. FILES UNDER REVIEW\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/Users/michelker