s two evidence-free placeholder findings; iteration 3 resolves those placeholders explicitly without rewriting append-only history.\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:exhausted-approaches -->\n## 9. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n### `checklist_evidence` (core): **fail, provisional** - validator success is real but does not establish pre-Overview ordering; final replay is scheduled for iteration 3. -- BLOCKED (iteration 1, 1 attempts)\n- What was tried: `checklist_evidence` (core): **fail, provisional** - validator success is real but does not establish pre-Overview ordering; final replay is scheduled for iteration 3.\n- Why blocked: Repeated iteration evidence ruled this direction out.\n- Do NOT retry: `checklist_evidence` (core): **fail, provisional** - validator success is real but does not establish pre-Overview ordering; final replay is scheduled for iteration 3.\n\n### `checklist_evidence`: fail, carried forward from fresh strict validation and uncited checked items. -- BLOCKED (iteration 4, 1 attempts)\n- What was tried: `checklist_evidence`: fail, carried forward from fresh strict validation and uncited checked items.\n- Why blocked: Repeated iteration evidence ruled this direction out.\n- Do NOT retry: `checklist_evidence`: fail, carried forward from fresh strict validation and uncited checked items.\n\n### `feature_catalog_code` and `playbook_capability`: not applicable, carried forward. -- BLOCKED (iteration 4, 1 attempts)\n- What was tried: `feature_catalog_code` and `playbook_capability`: not applicable, carried forward.\n- Why blocked: Repeated iteration evidence ruled this direction out.\n- Do NOT retry: `feature_catalog_code` and `playbook_capability`: not applicable, carried forward.\n\n### `spec_code` (core): **fail, provisional** - current `C1-P1-001` contradicts R3; final protocol replay is scheduled for iteration 3. -- BLOCKED (iteration 1, 1 attempts)\n- What was tried: `spec_code` (core): **fail, provisional** - current `C1-P1-001` contradicts R3; final protocol replay is scheduled for iteration 3.\n- Why blocked: Repeated iteration evidence ruled this direction out.\n- Do NOT retry: `spec_code` (core): **fail, provisional** - current `C1-P1-001` contradicts R3; final protocol replay is scheduled for iteration 3.\n\n### `spec_code` and `checklist_evidence`: active iteration-1 R3 mismatch carried forward without repeating the correctness scan. -- BLOCKED (iteration 2, 1 attempts)\n- What was tried: `spec_code` and `checklist_evidence`: active iteration-1 R3 mismatch carried forward without repeating the correctness scan.\n- Why blocked: Repeated iteration evidence ruled this direction out.\n- Do NOT retry: `spec_code` and `checklist_evidence`: active iteration-1 R3 mismatch carried forward without repeating the correctness scan.\n\n### `spec_code`: fail, carried forward from the current R3 contradiction. -- BLOCKED (iteration 4, 1 attempts)\n- What was tried: `spec_code`: fail, carried forward from the current R3 contradiction.\n- Why blocked: Repeated iteration evidence ruled this direction out.\n- Do NOT retry: `spec_code`: fail, carried forward from the current R3 contradiction.\n\n### A feature-catalog capability mismatch: outside the packet's declared target set. -- BLOCKED (iteration 3, 1 attempts)\n- What was tried: A feature-catalog capability mismatch: outside the packet's declared target set.\n- Why blocked: Repeated iteration evidence ruled this direction out.\n- Do NOT retry: A feature-catalog capability mismatch: outside the packet's declared target set.\n\n### A new finding for the generic performance `loadScript(src)` utility: its example call is a hardcoded trusted URL and no path from untrusted input is shown. -- BLOCKED (iteration 2, 1 attempts)\n- What was tried: A new finding for the generic performance `loadScript(src)` utility: its example call is a hardcoded trusted URL and no path from untrusted input is shown.\n- Why blocked: Repeated iteration evidence ruled this direction out.\n- Do NOT retry